netstat is deprecated; it is replaced by features in ss, ip, and nstat

netstat -s  # display packet and connection statistics by protocol
nstat  # iproute2 pacakge replacement for "netstat -s"

netstat -i  # show summary statistics for each interface, including error
   counts
ip -s link [show [eth0]] # iproute2 package replacement for "netstat -i"
ip -s -s link [show [eth0]] # show error counts by type of error
